        Deposit Bonds When Buying Brisbane Property: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A buyer has offered a deposit bond instead of cash. Before you agree, understand exactly what a deposit bond is, what risks it carries for you as the seller, and when it is reasonable to proceed.
      </p>
    </div>
